Author : Manik Mathesh
Date : Jan 2022

Features Implemented:
=====================
    - Dependency injection
    - MVVM pattern
    - Multi-threading
    - Practiced TDD approach for one complete unit (Home screen)
    - Unit test for Network, ViewModel and ViewController classes
    - Sample UI Test for HomeViewController
    - Created Mock responses
    - Demonstration of xib use
    - Pull to refresh TableView
    - App can support from iOS 13.0

Improvements:
============
    - Paging
    - Add Details screen
    
Note:
=====
    - Used apple's ituens apis "https://swapi.dev/api/planets/" and sample response is stored in "Planets.json" file.
